Title: [ANN]ğŸš€BITCOMO| CPA NETWORK on Blockchain - FOR SMARTCONTRACT PROJECTS AND ICOğŸš€
Body: We are making 1st CPA on blockchain. The uniqueness of project in transparrency between advertiser and publisher wich can not be achieved in common CPA networks. CPA network not equal advertising network. It's a network wich gives mutually beneficial cooperation between advertiser and publisher. Advertiser comes to CPA network with his project and says "guys I have good project and I need to promote it", his project enters into the database and publishers see it and if they like it they are promoting it in advertising networks, forums, social networks, etc. for a reward from targeted actions needed to advertiser(Cost Per Action). Bitcomo will be CPA network for other ICO projects promoting. Publishers will be getting rewards here for investments in ICO projects(Cost Per Investment), advertisers will get investments in their projects.  I hope I got your question right and answered to it.

But the main advantage of BM utility token is that it is firmly based on existing laws and regulation.

Author: Bitcomo
Title: [ANN]ğŸš€BITCOMO| CPA NETWORK on Blockchain - FOR SMARTCONTRACT PROJECTS AND ICOğŸš€
Body: Performance Marketing is a comprehensive term that refers to online marketing and advertising programs in which advertisers pay and marketing companies (affiliates) are paid when a specific action is completed (such as a sale, lead or click). Unlike other forms of traditional advertising where fees are paid up front and do not depend upon the success of the ads, advertisers in performance marketing only pay for successful transactions. This is the best business model for both, advertisers and publishers and Bitcomo gives you an opportunity to be a part of this model.

Title: [ANN]ğŸš€BITCOMO| CPA NETWORK on Blockchain - FOR SMARTCONTRACT PROJECTS AND ICOğŸš€
